*Installing dependencies in Debian7 Nodo1 (Pre-Configured Enviroment)*

pip install django==1.4

pip install cython
pip install git+http://github.com/numpy/numpy/
pip install git+http://github.com/scipy/scipy/

##### Clone Project eGetOpinion 3.0

git clone https://github.com/jjoc/getopinionated

##### Getting started (To Run Development Server)

python manage.py localserver


##### Notes for setting up a production server
##### Make sure to add a local_settings.py file.
##### Set up cronjob to call Voting every 5 minutes:

python manage.py updatevoting

#eGetOpinion 3.0 is Inspired at Jonas's P-) Getopinionated & Oscar's eCidadania & AZL Kiosk's CENATIC 



